# Event Scheduler App (Full Stack)

Full-stack Event Scheduler App using **Node.js + Express + MongoDB** with a simple static frontend (FullCalendar).

Features:
- User registration & login (JWT)
- Create / Edit / Delete events
- Calendar view (FullCalendar)
- Event list view
- Reminder job that can send emails (optional SMTP configuration)
- Docker & docker-compose included for quick local setup

---

## Project structure
(see repository tree in the root of this repo)

---

## Requirements
- Node.js v16+ (if running without Docker)
- MongoDB (local or Atlas) or use the provided `docker-compose` (recommended)
- Optional: SMTP credentials for real email reminders

---

## Quick start (with Docker Compose)
1. Copy `.env.example` into `server/.env` and edit (set `JWT_SECRET`).
2. From project root run:
   ```bash
   docker compose up --build
